<item>
            <title>[THRIFT-3415] include unistd.h conditionally</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/THRIFT-3415</link>
                <project id="12310800" key="THRIFT">Thrift</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;THeaderTransport.h includes unistd.h unconidionaly.&lt;br/&gt;
This breaks on non posix systems.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;The solution is to include it only when the corresponding define is set, like it is done in the rest of the codebase.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
